Replace Character in String | Replace all occurrences of a given character with another character. 

import java.util.*;
class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        String str = "Hello world";
        char ch = 'o';
        char replaceCh = 'x';
        System.out.println(str.replace(ch,replaceCh));
    }
}

output:
Hellx wxrld
